{"tid":806460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國議會推動「仇女」入罪 下週三表決","createTime":"2018-09-04T16:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T23:25:02.000Z","uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6366ebb69d4d8ad757b8e71cc2e44a367674a095","tid":806460,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國議會日前推動「厭女症」入法，考慮將「厭女症」納為仇恨犯罪的一種，9月12日將在議會中進行辯論與投票。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，這項被稱為「窺視癖犯罪」法案，是為遏止有人意圖偷拍女性的私密部位，如果嫌犯在事後態度有「厭女症」的傾向，法官將可能加重其刑，最高可加判2連有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n這個法案由英國國會議員，工黨的Stella Creasy提案；Creasy說，希望能將「厭女症」視為種族、殘疾、性向與宗教歧視的一種，能納入仇恨犯罪的範疇；Creasy呼籲國會議員支持法案，讓它得以在國會中投票表決，「以確保每個人都能安全的在街上行走，而不用隨時擔心遭人騷擾。」<br />\n<br />\n不過基於英國國會的慣例，國會通常只會表決由政府提出的「公共法案」，鮮少會通過議員提出的「私人法案」；所以，這個法案一度遭保守黨議員Christopher Chope的阻擾，他堅稱「基於一貫的立場，堅決反對『私人法案』。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然Chope阻擾法案的行為成功影響了立法的進度，但也讓他遭到輿論的撻伐；不過，這個法案獲得英國首相文翠珊與部分保守黨議員的支持，隨後英國的司法大臣也發表聲明支持推動「窺視癖犯罪」法案，表示「當局已經制訂好相關的法律，並決心推動立法；希望有助於保護女性，並有效的將加害人繩之於法。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2541287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2541287&d=x89%2FcoWTpXmQxXKwNzv8Ib%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d2d71a32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2541287&h=024ba013\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2541287</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：星島六月報過呢單<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/742660-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E5%8C%96%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F742660-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%258B%258D%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2598%25BB&d=x89%2FcoWTpXmQxXKwNzv8Ib%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=30519857\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F742660-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%258B%258D%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2598%25BB&h=9c109d7e\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/742660-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E5%8C%96%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB</a><br />\n<br />\nMay姐你都係收檔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6516154529dc039484af8b0560b48c95773dde","tid":806460,"uid":170229,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T21:30:15.000Z","msg":"這項被稱為「窺視癖犯罪」法案，是為遏止有人意圖偷拍女性的私密部位，如果嫌犯在事後態度有「厭女症」的傾向，法官將可能加重其刑<br />\n<br />\n厭女關偷拍咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f714b749a82a28cfa32e4fcb6f4638be7ee7f0aa","tid":806460,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T21:49:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"007867c1dff93c8abd6cde021678fe13ef03cab1","tid":806460,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T22:50:02.000Z","msg":"過到先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左膠黨一年推動幾百萬樣嘢啦"},{"pid":"6b4b4f8122859066dac7bc054a2df1ed27f04d23","tid":806460,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T22:55:22.000Z","msg":"D女權撚仇男<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218614394a61998a03312b99b7ec14f7516b195a","tid":806460,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T